data.description: Don't miss the incredible opportunity to own this centrally located single level home with mature landscaping, a backyard oasis and an open-concept layout. As you enter, a circular fireplace with a rich brick hearth takes center stage, creating an inviting ambiance between the great room and dining room. Crown molding and plantation shutters in the great room add a touch of elegance and sophistication to the living space. The galley kitchen is equipped with a suite of white appliances, including double ovens, a gas cooktop, dishwasher, and refrigerator. Whether you're preparing a casual meal or entertaining guests, this kitchen provides both functionality and style. Newer carpet has been installed in each of the four bedrooms. The spacious Arizona room boasts its own mini-split A/C system and French doors leading to the backyard, providing a seamless connection between indoor and outdoor living. Enjoy the backyard oasis featuring two ramadas/pergolas, flagstone patio and a sparkling and inviting pool. Step into the backyard oasis and discover two ramadas/pergolas, a flagstone patio, and a sparkling, inviting pool. The gated property features a fenced driveway with ample space for up to 6 cars, offering both convenience and security. The 2-car garage not only provides shelter for your vehicles but also offers generous storage space and includes laundry hookups. One notable feature of this property is its absence of an HOA, granting you the freedom to enjoy and personalize your home and surroundings according to your preferences.
